      "title": "The shot dies",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Saman Rohitha Perera aka \"Pas Podda\" who is said to be involved in several crimes and was receiving treatment in the intensive care unit of Gampaha Hospital after being seriously injured in a shooting that took place this afternoon in front of the Gampaha High Court, police say that he died a few moments ago.",
        "Dr. Saman Pathirana, director of the hospital, said that three others who were shot along with this person are receiving treatment at the Gampaha District General Hospital."
      ],
